reviewText: You can purchase all of the above movies for under $30.  DO NOT WASTE YOUR MONEY ON THIS PACK!  The movies are amazing though.

This is a great movie pack, and the price was really good as well.  Donnie Darko was a great movie. I had never seen it up until about 2 years ago and thought WOW this is a great movie.  I would say it is Jake Gyllenhaal's best performance Ive seen (I never did see Brokeback Mountain).  Boondock Saints was a great movie as well.  Willem Dafoe has a great role.  And of course the classic Edward Scissorhands.
